的获得成本不低，年轻人要打拼，经济、心理的压力都很大。 毕业后，留在大城市还是回到家乡？这个问题你怎么看？在本问题下参与讨论，优质回答者我们将送出黄灯《我的二本学生》新书一本，一共 5 个名额，快来参与吧！ 【活动截止时间】 2021 年 2 月 28 日 【参与方式】 在本问题下发表回答，即视为参与成功。【活动奖励】 黄灯《我的二本学生》新书一本。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-226154e09462fecb071290be6b6e9d1d_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "118 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/443012930"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I2uq74LaJifJjEAMaCDYwNzI1MjM0IOSU9IAGMAE43QRAKHIJNDQzMDEyOTMweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "41_1613757694.7773438", "card_id": "Q_443223947", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 36}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何以「我是暴君的婢女，刚替暴君挡了一剑」为开头写一篇文？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "114 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/443223947"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I2uq74LaJifJjEAMaCDYwNzcyMzk0IN70+oAGMAE4hQFAKXIJNDQzMjIzOTQ3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "42_1613757694.777572", "card_id": "Q_388752043", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 439}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有什么看着很舒服的微信背景图?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-49d81a7a35996653f7ebc9e37671c492_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "112 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/388752043"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I2uq74LaJifJjEAMaCDQ4NjY3MzA1IOK46vQFMAI4rTZAKnIJMzg4NzUyMDQzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "43_1613757694.7779346", "card_id": "Q_444915324", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 28}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价《一人之下》第 546 话？"}, "ex